SiF' Custom Upgrades List

At the time of writing this, these weapons were seen in;
• Metro - Pseudomachination (Hard Adv) -- 2024
• Scallops - Desonemebria (Easy Adv) -- 2025
• Saxford - (?) WIP
• Cyberia - 666(?) WIP
Most of these were only available in [REDACTED] servers. Reasoning not issued.

Notes:
Since they were intended to powerscale towards the intended missions, 
Most of these were designed to either provide a sidegrade of existing weapons or
provide a certain niche counterplay to existing robots in said mission.

