Primary
  	1. Scattergun
	 • A) (0$) Uplifter // [ +50 Accuracy | -40% Pellets ]
	 	 -- 
      Killstreaks Active, Sheen: Cool
      +50% more accurate

      -40% bullets per shot
	 • B) (200$) Scattercannon // [ +20% More Pellets | Beggar Reload, -33% DMG ]
	 	 -- 
      Killstreaks Active, Sheen: Hot
      Hold Fire to load up to 6 bullets
      +20% bullets per shot

      -33% damage penalty vs players
	 • C) (400$) Perceptionist // [ Combo: +40% More Pellets | -20% FireRate ]
	 	 -- 
      Killstreaks Active, Sheen: Isotope
      KillCombo: Gain up to +40% bullets per shot
      KillCombo: Gain up to +40% faster firing speed

      +20% slower firing speed

